CharToColor = function(input_char){ 
  mapping = c("1"="blue", "2"="red", "3"="yellow")
  mapping[input_char]
}
ad_data$DXCURREN.col = sapply(ad_data$DXCURREN, CharToColor)

plot(tsne_digits$Y, main="t-SNE Clusters", col=ad_data$DXCURREN.col, pch = 15)
